OL,3,CGovernment announces support for
OL,4,Cpollack fishers affected by zero-catch
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FFishermen affected by a zero catch
OL,8,Flimit on pollack will have
OL,9,Fapplications for Government grants
OL,10,Ffast-tracked, after warnings that the
OL,11,Fimpact on businesses could be
OL,12,F"devastating".
OL,14,FThe Government made the decision to
OL,15,Fset the pollack catch quota to zero
OL,16,Famid concerns about stock in the South
OL,17,FWest.
OL,19,FIt has been met with compensation from
OL,20,Ffishing businesses who claim they are
OL,21,Fstruggling to survive.
