OL,3,CGovernment announces support for
OL,4,Cpollack fishers affected by zero-catch
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FOn Friday 23 February, the Government
OL,8,Fmade an announcement in a bid to
OL,9,Frelieve pressure on affected
OL,10,Ffishermen, including faster processing
OL,11,Ftimes for applications for financial
OL,12,Fgrants.
OL,14,FThose who choose to apply to the
OL,15,FFisheries and Seafood Scheme will see
OL,16,Fthe processing time halved to four
OL,17,Fweeks, which the Government says will
OL,18,Fhelp fishermen diversify and explore
OL,19,Fnew ways to make a living.
