OL,3,CGovernment announces support for
OL,4,Cpollack fishers affected by zero-catch
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FA total of #6 million funding is
OL,8,Favailable through the scheme this year
OL,9,Ffor those who make fast-track
OL,10,Fapplications.
OL,12,FFisheries Minister, Mark Spencer MP,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We fully recognise the impact
OL,14,Fthat the bycatch-only pollack fishery
OL,15,Fhas had on many fishermen in the South
OL,16,FWest and today's measures will provide
OL,17,Fsupport to those most affected.
OL,19,F"Grant funding will help to support
OL,20,Fthem to diversify and explore other
OL,21,Fincome streams.
