OL,5,Climit
OL,7,F"Whilst their participation in a new
OL,8,Fscientific study will not only provide
OL,9,Fadditional support but help to improve
OL,10,Four understanding of the pollack stock
OL,11,Fas we look to improve its
OL,12,Fsustainability into the future."
OL,14,FThe scheme, which opened in 2021, will
OL,15,Fre-open for applications this month
OL,16,Fand applies for hand-and-pole line
OL,17,Ffishers of under-10m vessels.
